item arch "Arch Linux • Minimal, rolling, fully customizable
   “Control every variable, and the system never surprises you.” — Edward Nygma"

item alpine "Alpine Linux • Ultra‑light, musl‑based, container‑ready
   “Low power, low footprint — efficient by design.” — Pamela Isley"


item --gap -- ================== RARE / SPECIAL DISTROS ==================

item garuda "Garuda Linux • Performance‑tuned Arch system
   “Power is nothing without responsiveness.” — Dick Grayson"

item bazzite "Bazzite • Immutable Fedora‑based gaming OS
