item gparted "GParted Live • Partitioning & disk surgery
   “Precision is everything.” — Leslie Thompkins"

item clonezilla "Clonezilla • Imaging & cloning utility
   “Replication is the fastest form of preparedness.” — Lucius Fox"

item hirens "Hiren’s BootCD PE • Windows‑based rescue environment
   “Sometimes you need to speak the language of the world.” — Bruce Wayne"

item grml "GRML • Debian‑based rescue shell environment
